{"tid":2042683,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒！期待手持午餐肉就可以有西屌嘅日子","createTime":"2020-05-30T03:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T03:16:35.000Z","uid":154406,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"240c281bc2b76fc261a527927b417547c7c6e696","tid":2042683,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T03:07:51.000Z","msg":"取消獨立關稅地位又好,港元貶值又好,武漢肺炎再爆發又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,到有日真係出現全香港範圍MAP炮,就咩都唔使<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VEhyR1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVEhyR1F.jpg&h=eabd2945&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YLvpee4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYLvpee4.jpg&h=ee3c88ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開太多,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZXGgts.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZXGgts.jpg&h=3d4faedb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n停止供應東江水,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食麵有5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n全港停擺~~~<br />\n無網上~~無娛樂~~無野買無野食的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f6c2c1edb6f3723b6759e80a273cbd5dd37aa94","tid":2042683,"uid":13412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"果位巴打仲有冇補貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e66243d374b813e4883495b6c3fbcb209d6d57","tid":2042683,"uid":154406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6c2c1edb6f3723b6759e80a273cbd5dd37aa94","tid":2042683,"uid":13412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"果位巴打仲有冇